\c 8
\s Ubupristi bukaKristu bukhulu kulalobo obamaJuda
\p
\v 1 Ngakho isiqokoqela sezinto esazikhulumayo \add yikuthi\add*: Silompristi omkhulu\x + 3.1.\x* onje, owahlala ngakwesokunene\x + 1.3. Hlab. 110.1.\x* sesihlalo sobukhosi soMkhulu emazulwini\x + 4.14.\x*,
\v 2 isikhonzi\x + 1.7. 1.14.\x* se\add ndawo\add* ezingcwele\x + 9.2,8,12,24,25; 10.19; 13.11. 9.1.\x*\f + \fk indawo ezingcwele: \fl kumbe, \fq izinto ezingcwele.\f* lesethabhanekele eliqotho\x + 9.24. 9.11.\x*, iNkosi eyalimisayo\x + Eks. 33.7.\x*, njalo kungesimuntu;
\v 3 ngoba wonke umpristi omkhulu umiselwe ukunikela iminikelo lemihlatshelo\x + 5.1.\x*; ngakho kuyadingeka ukuthi laye abe lakho okuthile angakunikela\x + 9.14. Efe. 5.2.\x*.
\v 4 Ngoba uba ubesemhlabeni, ubengeyikuba ngumpristi lakanye, ngoba bakhona abapristi abanikela iminikelo ngokomlayo\x + 5.1.\x*,
\v 5 abakhonza isibonelo\x + 9.23.\x* lesithunzi sezinto zezulwini\x + 10.1. Kol. 2.17.\x*, njengoMozisi elaywe nguNkulunkulu esezakwenza ithabhanekele\x + 11.7. 12.25. Luka 2.26.\x*, ngoba wathi\x + 2.6.\x*: Qaphela\x + Eks. 25.40.\x* ukuthi wenze zonke izinto njengomfanekiso owaboniswa wona entabeni.
\v 6 Kodwa khathesi-ke uzuze inkonzo\x + 9.21. Luka 1.23.\x* enhle kakhulu\x + 1.4.\x*, njengalokhu laye engumlamuli\x + 9.15. 12.24. 1 Tim. 2.5.\x* wesivumelwano\x + Roma 9.4.\x*\f + \fk isivumelwano: \fl kumbe, \fq ithestamente.\f* esingcono\x + 7.22. 7.19.\x*, esimiswe phezu\x + 7.11.\x* kwezithembiso ezingcono\x + 7.22. 7.19.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Ngoba uba leso\add sivumelwano\add* esakuqala besingasoleki, bekungayikudingwa indawo yesesibili\x + 7.11,18.\x*.
\v 8 Ngoba ebasola uthi\x + 2.6.\x*: Khangela insuku ziyeza, kutsho iNkosi\x + Jer. 31.31-34.\x*, njalo ngizakwenza isivumelwano esitsha lendlu kaIsrayeli lendlu kaJuda;
\v 9 esingenjengesivumelwano engasenza laboyise\x + Roma 9.4.\x* mhla ngibabamba ngesandla ukubakhupha elizweni leGibhithe; ngoba bona kabahlalanga esivumelwaneni sami, lami kangibananzanga, itsho iNkosi\x + 2.16.\x*.
\v 10 Ngoba yilesi\x + 10.16. Roma 11.27.\x* isivumelwano\x + Roma 9.4.\x* engizavumelana ngaso lendlu kaIsrayeli emva kwalezonsuku, itsho iNkosi, ngizafaka\f + \fk ngizafaka: \fl kumbe, \fq ngizakupha.\f* imilayo yami engqondweni yabo, lenhliziyweni\f + \fk lenhliziyweni: \fl kumbe, \fq laphezu kwenhliziyo.\f* zabo ngiyibhale; ngibe nguNkulunkulu kibo, bona-ke bazakuba ngabantu kimi.
\v 11 Njalo kabayikufundisa ngulowo lalowo umakhelwane wakhe, njalo ngulowo lalowo umfowabo, esithi: Yazi iNkosi; ngoba bonke bazangazi, kusukela komncinyane wabo kuze kufike komkhulu wabo\x + Luka 22.29.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba ngizakuba lesihawu ekungalungini kwabo, lezono zabo lobubi babo kangisayikukukhumbula\x + 10.17.\x*.
\v 13 Ngokuthi: \add Isivumelwano\add* esitsha, senze esokuqala saba ngesigugileyo. Njalo osekugugile lokudala sekuseduze lokunyamalala\x + 6.8. 2 Kor. 5.17.\x*.
